claim: The Titanic's wreck is gradually disintegrating in a museum.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The wreck of Titanic , first discovered over 70 years after the sinking , remains on the seabed , split in two and gradually disintegrating at a depth of 12415 ft. Since her discovery in 1985 , thousands of artefacts have been recovered and put on display at museums around the world .
